# mpc
bindsym $mod+less 			exec exec mpc prev
bindsym $mod+Shift+less		exec exec mpc seek 0%
bindsym $mod+greater		exec exec mpc next
bindsym $mod+Shift+greater	exec exec mpc next

# For advancing forward/backward in an mpd song
bindsym $mod+bracketleft 		exec exec mpc seek -10
bindsym $mod+Shift+bracketleft	exec exec mpc seek -120
bindsym $mod+bracketright		exec exec mpc seek +10
bindsym $mod+Shift+bracketright	exec exec mpc seek +120

